    dc:description "FIGURES 1–4. Antennoseius perseus n. sp., female, phoretic form. 1, Dorsal shields; 2, Scanning electron micrograph of anterior portion of podonotal shield and most of leg I; 3, Ventral shields; 4, Tectum." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5241599/files/figure.png" ;
