<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5241601>
    dc:description "FIGURES 5–9. Antennoseius perseus n. sp., female, phoretic form. 5, Subcapitulum; 6, Scanning electron micrograph of palpcoxal seta; 7, Right chelicera, lateral (antiaxial) view; 8, Right leg I (except tarsus), postero-lateral view; 9, Right leg III, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5241601/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5241605>
