<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5241607>
    dc:description "FIGURES 14–15. Antennoseius perseus n. sp., female, free-living form. 14, Right leg I (except tarsus), postero-dorsal view; 15, Right leg III, postero-dorsal view." ;
